<subSubSection pageId="22" pageNumber="415" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="22.[124,1333,295,925]" pageId="22" pageNumber="415">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[127,475,728,761]" pageId="22" pageNumber="415">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Ixtlan Shrew was only recently described and is known from a relatively small distribution that is not fully resolved. More research is needed to make a proper assessment, but it is threatened by deforestation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
